[{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0199","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0199.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0224","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9169,\"outputTokens\":30,\"totalTokens\":10863}}","description":"SCO UnixWare 7.x 系统中 ARCserve 代理存在本地符号链接漏洞，攻击者可在 /tmp 目录创建恶意符号链接，诱导 ARCserve 进程以 root 权限写入关键文件，从而实现本地提权。该漏洞影响 SCO UnixWare 7.1 及 7.1.1 版本，需本地账户访问权限才可利用，CVSS 评分 1.2，属低危本地提权漏洞。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0224"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:15.793","remediation":"建议升级 SCO UnixWare 到 7.1.3 或更高版本并应用 ARCserve 补丁补丁包（如 ARCserve 6.61 SP2 或更高版本），或在 /tmp 目录设置粘滞位（chmod +t /tmp）限制符号链接创建，同时限制普通用户对 /tmp 的写入权限作为临时缓解措施","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-15&msg=000101bf78af%2494528870%244d2f45a1%40jmagdych.na.nai.com","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19752","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/786262dea273b0bddfc7eb6f6950f11b9f01c05c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0224.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0224","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0224.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/165075bb4c3675993ac058501ff8575bd07a9ca0/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0224.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f43f79d7ee652229af6058b1c98133bb5bbc17fb/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-88qx-39r7-wq45/GHSA-88qx-39r7-wq45.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88294/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/63d4031680b3d3fa77b826660a1e30ffc70ff5cd/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0224.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5a4dcab7-6803-401a-8eb5-0506de4c5125.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0199.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0199.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0199.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0147","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0147.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0167","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 Pickup 目录拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 的 Pickup 目录存在拒绝服务漏洞，本地攻击者可在该目录中创建文件名超长且扩展名为 .txt.eml 的邮件文件，导致 IIS 的 Inetinfo.exe 进程因无法正确处理畸形文件名而崩溃，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞仅需本地访问权限即可触发，攻击条件简单，影响 IIS 4.0 版本的 Web 服务可用性。CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0167"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:08.410","remediation":"升级至 IIS 5.0 或更高版本以彻底修复此漏洞；如无法升级，在 IIS 管理控制台中禁用 SMTP 服务的 Pickup 目录功能，或通过 NTFS 权限限制 Pickup 目录（默认路径 C:\\Inetpub\\mailroot\\Pickup）的写入权限，仅允许受信任的应用程序访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ntbugtraq.com/default.asp?pid=36&sid=1&A2=ind0002&L=ntbugtraq&F=&S=&P=8800","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20310","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/58316128f65d22a226717ff1f92ebf2058e46bc6/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0167.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0167","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0167.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0167.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/95e6ff620d5494b93ba2234edfcf6a45187dc0a8/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gmg7-xp25-93hp/GHSA-gmg7-xp25-93hp.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/2000/0xxx/cve-2000-0167.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0167.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--26d80389-5595-4b40-929f-5170b708523e.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001168.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0147.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0174","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0174.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0197","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 计划任务程序本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Windows NT 任务计划程序存在权限提升漏洞，当交互用户登录系统时，计划任务会使用当前用户的驱动器映射，本地攻击者可通过在原始批处理文件位置放置特洛伊木马批处理文件来替换原有文件，从而以更高权限执行恶意代码。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系统，需本地用户登录且具备文件替换权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0197"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-14T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:12.237","remediation":"升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统，Windows NT 4.0 已停止支持且不再提供安全更新。如无法升级，在任务计划程序中禁用交互式任务，避免计划任务使用当前登录用户的驱动器映射。限制本地用户对批处理文件所在目录的写入权限，防止替换为木马文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/ntbugtraq/current/0202.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1050","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8de487bef2c8b1936da1237463dc6052a1