攻击者伪造 227 响应绕过端口访问控制。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/328867","http://www.osvdb.org/4417","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/979","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0150.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0150","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0150.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0150.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjp8-g7wh-3846/GHSA-pjp8-g7wh-3846.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0150.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e6b37487-b863-4fe6-a16d-f14a8db9b7b8.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001166.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0134.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0408","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0408.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0141","title":"Infopop Ultimate Bulletin Board 远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Infopop Ultimate Bulletin Board（UBB）论坛系统在主题隐藏（topic hidden）字段的处理中存在命令注入缺陷，未对用户输入做充分过滤。远程攻击者可在该字段中插入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等），使服务器将其作为系统命令的一部分执行，从而在未授权的情况下运行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 UBB 的 Web 服务器，攻击者只需向论坛提交特制的请求即可触发，无需身份认证，危害等级为严重（CVSS 10.0）。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0141"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:05.100","remediation":"升级到 Infopop Ultimate Bulletin Board 5.43 或更高版本（厂商已修复该字段的 shell 元字符过滤）。如无法立即升级，应临时关闭论坛发帖功能或在 Web 服务器层（如通过 mod_security 规则）拦截包含分号、反引号、管道符等 shell 元字符的 topic 隐藏字段提交请求作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/991","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-22&msg=NDBBLKOPOLNKELHPDEFKIEPGCAAA.renzo.toma%40veronica.nl","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&date=2000-02-8&msg=20000211224935.A13236%40infomag.ape.relarn.ru","http://www.ultimatebb.com/home/versions.shtml","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0141.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0141","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0141/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0141.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0141.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g2jv-69ph-8q7w/GHSA-g2jv-69ph-8q7w.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0141.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001163.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7441a9d8-1c7b-40e1-8aaa-adf5ad7b04d9.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0408.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0127","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0127.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0143","title":"OpenSSH SSH服务端 端口转发隧道认证绕过 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"SSH 协议服务端 sshd 存在本地安全绕过漏洞。当系统配置为允许无交互式 shell 访问的本地用户登录时，sshd 未能正确限制此类用户的连接转发权限。攻击者（已拥有本地账户但无 shell 访问权限）可利用 sshd 的 TCP 连接转发功能，将连接重定向至使用系统标准密码数据库进行认证的本地服务（如 POP 或 FTP），从而绕过原本针对无 shell 用户访问限制的身份认证机制，以该用户身份访问受限服务。该漏洞影响使用 sshd 且启用 TCP 转发、并对部分本地用户禁用 shell 的 SSH 服务器部署环境，攻击前提为攻击者需先获得一个无 shell 权限的本地账户，CVSS 评分为 4.6，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0143"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:05.360","remediation":"升级到 SSH（OpenSSH/SSH Communications Security）2000年3月后发布的安全修复版本（如 OpenSSH 1.2.3p1 及以上，或对应厂商补丁）；在服务端 sshd_config 中禁用不安全的 TCP 转发（将 AllowTcpForwarding 设为 no），并限制无 shell 权限用户使用端口转发；同时关闭 POP/FTP 等服务对系统密码数据库的直接认证，改用独立认证机制作为缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0143","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0143.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0143.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0143","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/e8168d69b3ae53a8a727801448f04969d48cd746/2000/CVE-2000-0143.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0143.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mcq5-ghfg-w6qg/GHSA-mcq5-ghfg-w6qg.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0143.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/O/openssh_122.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x89000/88337/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001165.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0127.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0126","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0126.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0142","title":"Netopia Timbuktu Pro 远程控制认证协议拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Netopia Timbuktu Pro 远程控制软件 2.0b650 及 5.2.1 版本的认证协议存在安全缺陷，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标主机的 407 和 1417 端口发送大量连接请求，耗尽系统资源，导致目标服务拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Timbuktu Pro 系列远程控制软件，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等，攻击复杂度低，但仅影响服务可用性，不涉及数据泄露或权限提升。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0142"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-02-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:05.240","remediation":"升级 Timbuktu Pro 至 5.2.2 或更高版本（该版本修复了认证协议中的拒绝服务漏洞）。如无法升级，在防火墙或主机层面阻止对端口 407 和 1417 的未授权外部访问，仅允许可信 IP 连接。对于已停止支持的旧版本，建议迁移至替代远程控制方案。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-2000-0142","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19750","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/2000/CVE-2000-0142.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0142.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0142","https://github.com/sari3l/Poc-Monitor/blob/634779a1484dffc87947e325536a762c19a80895/2000/CVE-2000-0142.json","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/2000.txt","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-58hp-w4jf-r5x7/GHSA-58hp-w4jf-r5x7.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/b4ddb28f94d250449ab64c1617f45b1f91701fa2/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0142.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/984/info.html","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001164.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0126.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0125","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0125.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0140","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9135,\"outputTokens\":21,\"totalTokens\":10820}}","description":"True North Internet Anywhere Mail Server 3.1.3 的 POP3 服务存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程未认证攻击者可通过向 POP3 服务发起大量并发连接请求，耗尽服务器连接资源导致服务拒绝。该漏洞影响 True North Internet Anywhere Mail Server 3.1.3 版本的 POP3 服务组件，CVSS 评分 5.0（中等严重），攻击者无需认证即可远程发起攻击，通过发送大量连接请求耗尽服务器资源导致拒绝服务。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0140"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:04.987","remediation":"升级 True North Internet Anywhere Mail Server 至官方修复版本（3.1.4 及以上）。如暂无法升级，可在邮件服务器前端防火墙或路由器上限制单个源 IP 对 POP3（TCP 110 端口）的并发连接数与连接频率，并设置空闲连接超时断开，以缓解大量连接导致的拒绝服务攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95021326417936&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/980","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/68b3c685b96421db99cac9beb9d7bc8a6314be79/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0140.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0140","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0140.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0140.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/645f3b3aab113438413618cef41319453f39d643/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-rhrc-cc2w-crx2/GHSA-rhrc-cc2w-crx2.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0140.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001162.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/44b40554314aa90807d3ddee27488f8c21cbcd40/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0125.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0409","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0409.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0148","title":"MySQL 安全绕过漏洞","description":"MySQL 3.22 版本存在身份认证绕过漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 MySQL 服务发送特制的短校验字符串（short check string），绕过密码认证机制，未经授权访问目标数据库。该漏洞源于 MySQL 对认证校验字符串的处理缺陷，攻击者无需任何凭证即可利用，影响 MySQL 3.22 及可能的相关版本，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0148"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:06.007","remediation":"升级 MySQL 至 3.23 及以上版本，该漏洞已在 3.23 中修复。由于 MySQL 3.22 已停止维护，建议迁移至受支持的 MySQL 8.0+ 或 MariaDB 10.x 版本，并启用密码认证插件（如 mysql_native_password 或 caching_sha2_password）增强认证安全性。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-02/0053.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/975","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0148.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0148","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0148.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0148.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-mrff-5fq9-xcxc/GHSA-mrff-5fq9-xcxc.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/2000/0xxx/cve-2000-0148.yaml","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/M/mysql_bad_password.nasl","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152100_152200.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0148.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0409.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0132","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0132.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0147","title":"SCO OpenServer SNMPD 默认共享漏洞","description":"SCO OpenServer 系统的 SNMPD 服务存在默认 SNMP 团体字符串可写漏洞。由于安装时未修改默认 SNMP 读写团体字符串（如 \"public\"、\"private\"），本地攻击者可通过 SNMP 协议直接修改目标主机的系统配置参数，包括网络设置、服务状态等。该漏洞影响 SCO OpenServer 系列操作系统，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，但可被用于进一步扩大攻击面。建议管理员修改默认 SNMP 团体字符串或禁用 SNMP 服务。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0147"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-02-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:05.877","remediation":"修改 /etc/snmpd.conf 配置文件，将默认读写 community 字符串（如 \"private\"）改为复杂随机字符串，并设置 read-only community 仅用于监控。在 /etc/hosts.allow 和防火墙层面限制 SNMP（UDP 161/162）只允许受信管理 IP 访问。如业务不需要 SNMP 服务，建议直接禁用 snmpd 守护进程。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-02/0045.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/973","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/42b5b7a8a9b34b1b292b9bfd27242e499ccb6cb9/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0147.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0147","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0147.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/21d84550d4f5d6b78cac9f7c41b1b20a874c9f15/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0147.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cve-reference-ingest-data/blob/6945e76faad488b458876e7ec12ebf0f2c4be89c/references/CVE-2000-0147-2023-09-21-1730","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/05/GHSA-rj5j-5wh3-4g3p/GHSA-rj5j-5wh3-4g3p.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/973/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0147.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_