:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:03.530","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 Daniel Beckham Finger Server 0.82 Beta 服务，该版本存在命令注入漏洞且已停止维护。如必须使用 Finger 协议，建议替换为支持输入过滤的现代实现（如 inetutils-finger），并在防火墙层面限制仅允许受信 IP 访问 TCP 79 端口。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.glazed.org/finger/changelog.txt","http://www.osvdb.org/7610","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19745","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8de487bef2c8b1936da1237463dc6052a1fcd655/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0128.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0128","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0128/README.md","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-2000-0128.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/263f37bc67cd24fe03a39077d8b57f3001369a95/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0128.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5mgh-j8px-8cgf/GHSA-5mgh-j8px-8cgf.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0128.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/fankh/vulnerability-poc/blob/8854c056beab250ba690e2bcc8887feb4c1f8139/2000/CVE-2000-0128/README_KO.md"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0333.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0333.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0116","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0116.toml","cve